autocmd FileType css setlocal tabstop=2 shiftwidth=2 softtabstop=2
autocmd FileType javascript setlocal tabstop=2 shiftwidth=2 softtabstop=2


" indent/unindent with tab/shift-tab
nmap <Tab> >>
